query: WITH entities AS (SELECT key, id FROM core_domain_configs WHERE COALESCE(visibility = $1, $1 IS NULL) AND (COALESCE((key, id) > ($4, $3), $3 IS NULL)) ORDER BY key ASC, id ASC LIMIT $2) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: Repo__Id", e.sequence, e.event, CASE WHEN $5 THEN e.context ELSE NULL::jsonb END as "context: es_entity::ContextData", e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN core_domain_config_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.key asc, i.id asc, i.id, e.sequence
